downloadTitle: Send to Sway Add-In for OneNote (Preview)
downloadDescription: An Add-In for OneNote that allows users to send their content to Sway
detailsSection: The “Send to Sway” Add-in lets you easily create a new Sway from the images and text of the selected OneNote page. This turns the thoughts you’ve organized in OneNote into an interactive, visually compelling digital story in one click
systemRequirementsSection:
Operating System: Windows 7, 8, 8.1, or 10.
Microsoft OneNote 2013 or 2016 must be installed.
installInstructionSection: Select the platform version of the add-in that corresponds to your OneNote installation. If you have an x86 (or 32-bit) version of OneNote, then download the x86 version. If you have an x64 version of OneNote, download the x64 version.
